channel.title: **Magic Mushroom~(F2p Pking Server)**!#Fast Training~~**%100x exp rate%%%
channel.description:
Heya people! Magic Mushroom is back and coded to a [b][u]F2p Pking Server!![/u][/b] woo hoo ye! Loads of fun with f2p pking! It will mostly be low lvl f2p pking probably sense most people don't like lvl 123 pking.
[b][u]Updates[/u][/b]
*full rune and r2h's can be bought in varrock general store
*full working master fisher(gives out lobbs)
*full working adventurer
*Full working shops
*moss giants drop r2hs + str ammys, Moss giants are located in edgeville dungeon
*commands: ::edge and :: stuck
*start out with iron 2h in edgeville bank
*100x exp rate FAST TRAINING~!!
Server is a edited EasyRSC v1.1 source. If you do manage to get a hold of a member object it will be no use because the only member object you'll get a hold of is something like a cup of tea lol.
You cannot log in if you have spaces in your name, Sense it is a EasyRSC source. Come now, We are going to have are Easter event TODAY, to find out more info check forums! Hope i see you all there. [img]http://img19.imageshack.us/img19/12/joinmmonline.jpg[/img]
